# Bug Report Enhancer — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A full-stack **Bug Report Enhancer** tool matching your wireframes:

| Component | Tech | File |
|---|---|---|
| Backend | Express + TypeScript | [server.ts](file:///d:/New%20folder/Antigravity%20Sample/server.ts) |
| Frontend UI | HTML5 | [index.html](file:///d:/New%20folder/Antigravity%20Sample/public/index.html) |
| Styles | CSS (dark theme) | [style.css](file:///d:/New%20folder/Antigravity%20Sample/public/style.css) |
| Frontend Logic | TypeScript | [app.ts](file:///d:/New%20folder/Antigravity%20Sample/public/app.ts) |

### Key Features
- **Drag & Drop** screenshot upload with preview
- **Groq AI Analysis** using **Llama 4 Scout** (free tier) to auto-generate structured bug reports
- **Jira Integration** — creates issues with title, description, steps, severity, expected/actual behavior
- **Settings Modal** with separate **Test Connection** buttons for both Jira and Groq
- Premium dark theme with glassmorphism, gradients, and micro-animations

---

