## How to Run

```bash
# From project directory
npm install
npx tsc --outDir public --target ES2020 --module ES2020 --moduleResolution node --skipLibCheck --lib ES2020,DOM public/app.ts
npx ts-node server.ts
# Open http://localhost:3000 in Chrome
```

## Next Steps (Manual by User)
1. Open Settings → enter your **Groq API key** → click "Test Groq Connection"
2. Enter **Jira** URL, Project, Email, API Token → click "Test Jira Connection"
3. Save Settings
4. Upload a bug screenshot → click "Analyze & Push to Jira"
